title: Rongcheng Stadium
text: Rongcheng Stadium is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Rongcheng%2C%20Shandong">Rongcheng</a>, <a href="China">China</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches. The stadium holds 30,000 spectators.
